<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>All Posts - xtualong 的博客</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/</link><description>All Posts | xtualong 的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>VMware ESXi Ubuntu 虚拟机库依赖缺失导致服务启动失败</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/vmware-esxi-ubuntu-%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E5%BA%93%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 11:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>xtualong</author><guid>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/vmware-esxi-ubuntu-%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA%E5%BA%93%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%BC%BA%E5%A4%B1%E5%AF%BC%E8%87%B4%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E5%A4%B1%E8%B4%A5/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/esxi-depfix.svg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>Ubuntu 从 20.04 升级到 24.04 后，libcurl 与 libnghttp2 版本不匹配，导致 NetworkManager 启动时符号解析失败而崩溃，大量依赖网络的服务连锁失败。本文记录通过离线方式修复库依赖缺失、恢复系统服务的完整排查与解决过程。</p></blockquote>]]></description></item><item><title>VMware ESXi Ubuntu 虚拟机 fsck 修复文件系统损坏</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/vmware-esxi-ubuntu-%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA-fsck-%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%8D%9F%E5%9D%8F/</link><pubDate>Sun, 31 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>xtualong</author><guid>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/vmware-esxi-ubuntu-%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E6%9C%BA-fsck-%E4%BF%AE%E5%A4%8D%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%8D%9F%E5%9D%8F/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/esxi-fsck.svg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>ESXi 平台上的 Ubuntu 虚拟机因异常关机导致 ext4 文件系统损坏，开机后自动进入 <code>(initramfs)</code> 紧急 Shell 无法正常启动。本文记录从问题现象分析到使用 <code>fsck</code> 手动修复文件系统的完整处理流程，以及 ESXi 平台上的最佳实践建议。</p></blockquote>]]></description></item><item><title>Hermes Agent + Open WebUI Docker 部署指南</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/hermes-agent-+-open-webui-docker-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link><pubDate>Sun, 24 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>xtualong</author><guid>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/hermes-agent-+-open-webui-docker-%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/docker-ai.svg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>基于 Docker Compose 一键部署 Hermes Agent 网关与 Open WebUI 聊天界面，以小米 MiMo API + 微信网关为实例完成全流程配置。本文涵盖环境准备、Hermes Agent 配置、容器编排及 Open WebUI 接入的完整步骤。</p></blockquote>]]></description></item><item><title>小米路由器 OpenWrt 跨网段路由转发教程</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8-openwrt-%E8%B7%A8%E7%BD%91%E6%AE%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>xtualong</author><guid>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8-openwrt-%E8%B7%A8%E7%BD%91%E6%AE%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E8%BD%AC%E5%8F%91%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/openwrt-router.svg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>记录如何在小米路由器 BE6500 上刷入 OpenWrt 系统，实现跨网段路由转发的完整教程。涵盖固件刷写、网络配置、路由表设置，打通有线与无线网络间的通讯。</p></blockquote>]]></description></item><item><title>Ubuntu 24.04 手动升级 Linux 内核至 7.0 完整教程</title><link>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/ubuntu-24.04-%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7-linux-%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8%E8%87%B3-7/</link><pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 10:00:00 +0800</pubDate><author>xtualong</author><guid>https://www.xtualong.cn/posts/ubuntu-24.04-%E6%89%8B%E5%8A%A8%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7-linux-%E5%86%85%E6%A0%B8%E8%87%B3-7/</guid><description><![CDATA[<div class="featured-image">
                <img src="/images/linux-kernel.svg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">
            </div><blockquote>
<p>Ubuntu 24.04 LTS 服务器手动升级主线内核至 7.0，修复 CVE-2026-31431 高危漏洞。从 6.8.0-111-generic 升级至 7.0.0-15-generic 的完整操作记录，涵盖下载、安装、验证全流程。</p></blockquote>]]></description></item></channel></rss>